article.description: — Matt Cerruti had 15 points as Albany got past Hartford 71-52 on Saturday.
article.headline: Cerruti scores 15 to carry Albany past Hartford 71-52
article.linkText: Cerruti scores 15 to carry Albany past Hartford 71-52
article.story: WEST HARTFORD, Conn. -- — Matt Cerruti had 15 points as Albany got past Hartford 71-52 on Saturday. Jamel Horton had 14 points for the Great Danes (10-13, 6-5 America East Conference). Trey Hutcheson added eight rebounds. Moses Flowers had 11 points for Hartford (5-14, 3-4). ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/hub/college-basketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
